text: Oma Mua Oma Mua ('own land') is a Karelian-language newspaper published in Republic of Karelia. First issue was published in 1990 by Periodika. ==See also== *Karjalan Sanomat *Vienan Karjala ==References== == External links == * Category:Karelian language Category:Newspapers published in Russia
